(1, 1, '2016-06-14 15:03:24', '2016-06-14 18:03:24', 'Bem-vindo ao WordPress. Esse √© o seu primeiro post. Edite-o ou exclua-o, e ent√£o comece a escrever!', 'Ol√°, mundo!', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'ola-mundo__trashed', '', '', '2016-06-14 18:19:01', '2016-06-14 21:19:01', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tonca/wordpress/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(2, 1, '2016-06-14 15:03:24', '2016-06-14 18:03:24', 'Esta √© uma p√°gina de exemplo. √â diferente de um post porque ela ficar√° em um local e ser√° exibida na navega√ß√£o do seu site (na maioria dos temas). A maioria das pessoas come√ßa com uma p√°gina de introdu√ß√£o aos potenciais visitantes do site. Ela pode ser assim:\n\n<blockquote>Ol√°! Eu sou um bike courrier de dia, ator amador √† noite e este √© meu blog. Eu moro em S√£o Paulo, tenho um cachorro chamado Tonico e eu gosto de caipirinhas. (E de ser pego pela chuva.)</blockquote>\n\nou assim:\n\n<blockquote>A XYZ foi fundada em 1971 e desde ent√£o vem proporcionando produtos de qualidade a seus clientes. Localizada em Valinhos, XYZ emprega mais de 2.000 pessoas e faz v√°rias contribui√ß√µes para a comunidade local.</blockquote>\nComo um novo usu√°rio do WordPress, voc√™ deve ir at√© o <a href="http://localhost/tonca/wordpress/wp-admin/">seu painel</a> para excluir essa p√°gina e criar novas p√°ginas com seu pr√≥prio conte√∫do. Divirta-se!', 'P√°gina de Exemplo', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'pagina-exemplo__trashed', '', '', '2016-06-14 18:19:18', '2016-06-14 21:19:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tonca/wordpress/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(3, 1, '2016-06-14 15:03:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 'Rascunho autom√°tico', '', 'auto-draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2016-06-14 15:03:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tonca/wordpress/?p=3', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4, 1, '2016-06-14 15:06:28', '2016-06-14 18:06:28', '<p>Your Name (required)<br />\r\n    [text* your-name] </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your Email (required)<br />\r\n    [email* your-email] </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Subject<br />\r\n    [text your-subject] </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your Message<br />\r\n    [textarea your-message] </p>\r\n\r\n<p>[submit "Send"]</p>\nTheme Default "[your-subject]"\n[your-name] <renanemigdiogoncalves@hotmail.com>\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n--\r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Theme Default (http://localhost/tonca/wordpress)\nrenanemigdiogoncalves@hotmail.com\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\nTheme Default "[your-subject]"\nTheme Default <renanemigdiogoncalves@hotmail.com>\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n--\r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Theme Default (http://localhost/tonca/wordpress)\n[your-email]\nReply-To: renanemigdiogoncalves@hotmail.com\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.', 'Form #1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '